---
description: Self-review against acceptance criteria
allowed-tools: [Read, Bash, Glob, Grep]
---

Read ../../analysis/acceptance-criteria.md and verify each acceptance criterion.

## Tasks

For each AC item:
1. Verify the feature's code exists (using Grep, Glob)
2. Code review to confirm correct implementation (Read related files)
3. Pass/fail determination

## Result Handling
- If any items fail, create a list and pass to /iterate.
- If all items pass, output "Implementation complete" message.

## Check Format
```
- [x] AC-001: [description] — PASS
- [ ] AC-002: [description] — FAIL: [reason]
```
